# Tier 9.4: Loop with Iteration Variable
# Tests loop with index tracking using "as" syntax

# Build a story incrementally with iteration awareness
session "Start a short story with an opening sentence about a mysterious door."

loop until **the story has a satisfying conclusion** (max: 4) as chapter:
  session "Continue the story. This is chapter/iteration number. Add 2-3 sentences that advance the plot toward a conclusion."
    context: chapter

# Wrap up
session "Review the complete story above and give it a fitting title."
